{"tid":633133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"滙豐網上跨行轉賬免收費","createTime":"2018-04-18T04:42:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-03T12:01:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":60,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"3393d1fd8c3b8853c2a8a06747a56442cb15f97d","tid":633133,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T04:42:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180418/20365061?_ga=2.108169090.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180418%2F20365061%3F_ga%3D2.108169090.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&d=3BDfBKm6Na1HOiHBfCacPQdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=18b12c4d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180418%2F20365061%3F_ga%3D2.108169090.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171&h=cb36d35a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180418/20365061?_ga=2.108169090.1029761066.1520127978-1555213041.1517019171</a><br />\n<br />\n滙豐網上跨行轉賬免收費<br />\n<br />\n21.2K<br />\n要聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180418/large/18422045.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180418%2Flarge%2F18422045.jpg&h=0d826047&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nHSBC網上跨行轉賬下月起免收費。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】滙豐宣佈下月1日起調整銀行服務收費。個人客戶於網上理財或流動理財，透過「即時支付結算系統」跨行轉賬，將豁免收費，現時透過該電子渠道轉賬費用為每筆55元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下月起實施<br />\n<br />\n現時電子轉賬有削減費用趨勢。以匯豐旗下個人對個人（P2P）小額轉賬應用程式PayMe為例，並不收取任何費用；處理大額轉賬的網上電子渠道費用亦減至零。個人客戶收取經「即時支付結算系統」予滙豐戶口的款項，下月起亦將豁免現時每筆15元的費用。不過，若果在分行辦理跨行轉賬費用仍保持不變，每筆款項為200元。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，滙豐另一轉賬渠道「電子結算」，早於2016年已經豁免收費，不過該渠道結算時間較長，若果今日過數，後日才會成功轉賬（俗稱T+2）。而是次「即時支付結算系統」則是即時轉賬，有助解決客戶「痛點」，不過網上轉賬前，仍需要先經過認證，例如通過流動保安編碼，才能登記對方戶口。<br />\n<br />\n恒生銀行發言人表示正就有關收費進行檢討，渣打則表示不時檢討服務收費，中銀表示不時檢討各項收費政策，並會綜合考慮多項因素，如市場情況、客戶需求等。<br />\n<br />\n另外，滙豐亦削減電匯收費，個人客戶經滙豐網上理財辦理滙出款項，每次收費由115元，下月起減至65元；透過分行辦理電滙的費用將保持不變，根據網頁顯示為240元。<br />\n<br />\n■記者周家誠"},{"pid":"a465f4ad36740c717fd1f01639970b61386e1132","tid":633133,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:00:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93e2b2eafeeabc1799afc3db28db6b0c602517a1","tid":633133,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"真心求指教：咁可唔可以轉賑去第二間銀行交卡數？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：而家個個月用攞現金交卡數"},{"pid":"f639b258f7efb7b92764be5fbf2cae3529548a54","tid":633133,"uid":18948,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"93e2b2eafeeabc1799afc3db28db6b0c602517a1","tid":633133,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"真心求指教：咁可唔可以轉賑去第二間銀行交卡數？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：而家個個月用攞現金交卡數"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"c40b123d2b4433d651a5e5004de8e1edee660cdf","tid":633133,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"f639b258f7efb7b92764be5fbf2cae3529548a54","tid":633133,"uid":18948,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"93e2b2eafeeabc1799afc3db28db6b0c602517a1","tid":633133,"uid":103325,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:05:42.000Z","msg":"真心求指教：咁可唔可以轉賑去第二間銀行交卡數？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：而家個個月用攞現金交卡數"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:07:17.000Z","msg":"yes"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-18T05:08:55.000Z","msg":"thanks 巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e496bd1fbac11950f9c6fcab3f1b6ae01df832f","tid":633133,"uid":133522,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"quote":{"pid":"f639b258f7efb7b9276